(define/contract (circular-game-losers n k)
  (-> exact-integer? exact-integer? (listof exact-integer?))

  (define (next-position current-pos step n)
    (modulo (+ current-pos step) n))

  (define (find-losers n k)
    (let loop ([i 1] 
               [current-pos 0] 
               [received-ball (make-vector n #f)] 
               [ball-received-twice #f])
      (when (not ball-received-twice)
        (let ([next-pos (next-position current-pos (* i k) n)])
          (if (vector-ref received-ball next-pos)
              (set! ball-received-twice #t)
              (vector-set! received-ball next-pos #t))
          (loop (+ i 1) next-pos received-ball ball-received-twice)))
      (let ([losers '()])
        (for ([j n])
          (unless (vector-ref received-ball j)
            (set! losers (cons (+ j 1) losers))))
        (reverse losers))))

  (find-losers n k))
